<br>
With the new upgrade to detect hidden I spotted 2 stealthers standing right in front of the gate.  Scared the holy crud out of me until i notice they were from Alb. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    Nizar (assassin) and Lorandiel (sp?) (Minstrel).  5 seconds later a peewee archer from midgard comes running through..... and about 2 seconds later he is dead.  Heh.<br>
<br>
I start talking with Niz and Lor and end up joining their group.  3 stealthers slinking around the Middie port fort!  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Summary of my nights experiences:<br>
1) chalked up 309 RPs for my first night out (most due to being grouped but hey... i helped! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  )<br>
2) got my first solo kill on a red con healer.<br>
3) got 1-shotted 2x by the same assassin due to bone head situations.  (see below)<br>
4) danced with my first high level enemy assassin and came away alive<br>
5) engaged a purple con archer to provide a nearby cleric an escape.... and i ended up escaping myself (god i love stealth)<br>
6) made some new friends and had a SHITE load of fun.<br>
<br>
<br>
Details on the red con kill:  <br>
A group of at least 5 (think it was 6) comes down the valley from the middie port fort (people are crazy.... everyone uses the roads!!!)  I didnt notice that niz and lor had moved down to the road in position so i was a tad late on getting into the battle.  it actually worked out because the enemy group didnt realize there was another assassin loose <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
<br>
Im stealthing down the slope and notice one of the middies casting a heal spell (tell-tale blue lights from the fingers) so i make a b-line for her.  positioned in front while shes casting... hit /stick and BAM! slice her for a 154 hit PA with a 45 crit.  she started to run and realized i had linked her so she turned toe to toe with me!  the rapier and gauche where flying so fast you couldnt tell which one was from the other!! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Every spell cast was interupted (lucky me).  2 instas got off however but in short order the healer was no match.  soon as the healer was down i noticed only one more of their group alive...  a big ugly purp con troll.  with 2 assassins and a bard on him he went down fast.<br>
<br>
I can only imagine the look on her face when she realized she had just been killed by a blue con sacaren <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
<br>
The one shots:<br>
Later on into our hunting we were joined by another assassin from Niz and Lor's guild.  We met up with a bit larger force and the new arival was killed.  3 infi's and a bard makes a rezzing class not!  We told him not to release and to let us see if a rezzr was near... i know that tavish was around the area and started to send him a tell.... for some reason i stopped to send the message.  :O  Rule number one..... never stand still in rvr land!!  I had about 1 second visual on my killer before I bit the dirt..... Slythe a level 48 assassin.  Since my chat box was engaged I wasnt able to use my hotkeys to start an attack to reveal him. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Shot number 2.... Slythe had some friends come out to help play with us healerless albs.  we had added a mezzer and another infiltrator (yes count that 4 infiltrators now) and an armsman.  We were waiting in ambush at their MF gate.  Im hidden between the doors waiting for a stealther to come through..... nothing... i peak around the corner and see a troll casting a spell too far away.... im thinking they are buffing up. I have a visual on 4 and i know theres at least 1 stealther around.  I hide back behind the door.......... nothing.  This is where i make mistake number 2 of the night.... i peak back around the corner.  Just as i clear the post 2 stealthers pop into my vision.  Slythe again and an archer.  Low and behold i positioned myself right in front of him so he could get off a nice PA. :O  <br>
<br>
<br>
All in all I had a great time.  And it was mostly due to Nizar and Lorandiel!  Although Im only 30 I did notice Lots of orange and red con people out there.  Give me a few more levels and emain may be a regular hangout for me  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
<br>
